{"tid":2243124,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特首辦：林鄭月娥新型肺炎檢測結果呈陰性","createTime":"2020-10-14T13:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T14:11:36.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4d731a99eccfe85ae7e26f5c69b1d1100a7ce07f","tid":2243124,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:29:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554760-20201014.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554760-20201014.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiYm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=70df6635\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554760-20201014.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=17ee162d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554760-20201014.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n香港管弦樂團一名樂師初步確診新型肺炎，他曾在上周五及周六於文化中心參與演出，他負責吹奏單簧管，無法戴口罩，上星期五曾出席音樂會的行政長官林鄭月娥，對新型肺炎病毒檢測結果呈陰性。<br />\n<br />\n特首辦回應查詢時表示，行政長官前兩天已不只一次接受檢測，結果呈陰性，並會遵從衞生防護中心的健康建議，上星期五出席香港管弦樂團演出的特首辦隨行人員，亦會接受檢測。<br />\n<br />\n民政事務局局長徐英偉當晚到後台探班，已接受檢測，預計最快明天有結果。據了解，徐英偉今早如常上班，有結果前會取消公眾活動。同台演出約90多名樂師被界定為密切接觸者，要接受強制檢疫。"},{"pid":"ee1e9127baa4e3063ac20305d5ffd0dcd01ca515","tid":2243124,"uid":288913,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:47:14.000Z","msg":"有空窗期<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f777a72e6211bf3f808267dd7f2b5efc96dc003","tid":2243124,"uid":128287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:56:48.000Z","msg":"冇天理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42149012e16f2370844217604a2ff8d640d8f2d","tid":2243124,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img s